"функции присутствует в <literal>WHERE</literal> (Том Лейн)"

#. 2015-09-23 [cfb2024] Tom Lane: Make ANALYZE compute basic statistics even for..
#: release-9.5.xml:2204(para)
msgid ""
"Make <command>ANALYZE</command> compute basic statistics (null fraction and "
"average column width) even for columns whose data type lacks an equality "
"function (Oleksandr Shulgin)"
msgstr ""
"<command>ANALYZE</command> теперь вычисляет основную статистику (процент "
